{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-10-05-how-to-change-link-size-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aHoisting! To change link size in react js, you can set  in . It will change link size in react js. Today, I am going to show you, how‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To change link size in react js, you can set <code class=\"language-text\">font-size: 24px;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">.large-link</code>. It will change link size in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to change link size in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h2>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h2>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 2: Import react component.</h2>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 3: Create a Component.</h2>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">className=\"large-link\"</code> to change link size in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://ahoisting.com/\"</span> className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"large-link\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  aHoisting\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Change link size example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">'./App.css'</code> and set <code class=\"language-text\">font-size: 24px;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">.large-link</code> to change link size in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">App</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://ahoisting.com/\"</span> className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"large-link\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      aHoisting\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.css</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* App.css */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.large-link</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 24px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">font-size: 24px;</code> to change link size in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 306px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d031e13e3e2619ae116131c442482af1/3fb41/change-link-size.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.41772151898735%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRlYAAABXRUJQVlA4IEoAAABwAwCdASoUAA8APtFYpEwoJSOiMAgBABoJQApgAPOJ0dkjtMAA/VP1C5s76Ac5n3xxe7hPmWE/xNgPOIOjNZM0qzmTdBvwASQAAA=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, change, link, size\"\n        title=\"React, change, link, size\"\n        src=\"/static/d031e13e3e2619ae116131c442482af1/3fb41/change-link-size.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d031e13e3e2619ae116131c442482af1/81b7c/change-link-size.webp 158w,\n/static/d031e13e3e2619ae116131c442482af1/3fb41/change-link-size.webp 306w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to change link size in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"October 05, 2024","description":"Example of change link size in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change link underline color in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-10-06-how-to-change-link-underline-color-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change input background color in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-10-04-how-to-change-input-background-color-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2024-10-05-how-to-change-link-size-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2024-10-06-how-to-change-link-underline-color-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2024-10-04-how-to-change-input-background-color-in-react-js/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2555585279","2714594843","3159585216"]}